---
title: Ginger & Tamarind Tofu Noodles with Asian Greens & Peanut-Cashew Mix
description: This fragrant meal packs oodles of flavour into every mouthful. With Southeast Asian spices on the tofu and aromatic tamarind paste in the coconut sauce, plus crunchy crushed nuts to top it all off, this beats takeaway hands down.
